      "role": "user",
      "content": "i get the resistance thing but it just feels like so much unnecessary stuff in my body when the actual problem is solved. i read somewhere that taking antibiotics when you don't strictly need them can actually mess up your gut microbiome and cause more issues later on. if the symptoms are 100% gone, isn't it better to just stop now and save my body from the extra chemicals?",
